AQI values and their corresponding categories are as follows: 
   - Good: 0-50; 
   - Moderate: 51-100; 
   - Unhealthy for Sensitive Groups: 101-150; 
   - Unhealthy: 151-200; 
   - Very Unhealthy: 201-300; 
   - Hazardous: 301 and above. 
"Recently" refers to the most recent access within the last 30 days.

sql:
SELECT MAX(concentration_value) AS max_concentration, units
FROM pollutant_concentrations
WHERE pollutant_id = 1;

SELECT AVG(aqi_stat_value) AS average_aqi_90th_percentile
FROM aqi_statistics
WHERE station_id = 1 AND year = 2023 AND aqi_stat_name = 'AQI 90th Percentile';
